{"tid":1674174,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"遊民遭活活打死！「口插木棍」死狀超慘…凶手竟是2名男童","createTime":"2019-10-25T05:09:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T07:47:18.000Z","uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c287e52abd88c3900ba9a74dde39762731a32e0a","tid":1674174,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:09:50.000Z","msg":"烏克蘭一名遊民日前被發現陳屍在路邊，不僅頭部有遭到嚴重毆打的跡象，且口中還插著凶器木棍，死狀十分淒慘，沒想到，兇手竟是2名只有12歲的男童，且被逮捕時還毫無悔意地表示：「只是為了好玩。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VnbnAxi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVnbnAxi.jpg&h=4d0e1b77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n綜合俄媒報導，一名56歲的遊民亞歷山大（Александр）日前在烏克蘭比利萊夫卡（Беляевка）被發現陳屍在路邊，警方調閱監視器後，發現兇手竟是2名年僅12歲的男童。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1aa0ncx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1aa0ncx.jpg&h=feea7a3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這2名男童當天經過亞歷山大時，看見他正在翻找垃圾桶，竟突然拿起石塊向他丟擲，還持棍棒不斷毆打他，最後甚至拿著石塊狂砸他的後腦勺，亞歷山大面對突如其來的攻擊根本無力反擊，只能倒在地上任憑他們毆打。2名男童離去時，把石塊放在遊民臉上，還將毆打亞歷山大的棍棒插在他的口中。醫護人員到場時，試圖想急救亞歷山大，最後卻仍回天乏術。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/peMCpq4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpeMCpq4.jpg&h=5d7da8a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n這2名男童被逮捕歸案後，被問及行兇原因，竟毫無悔意地說：「只是因為好玩。」警方調查後發現，男童的家庭狀況似乎不太正常。<br />\n <br />\n亞歷山大生前雖然每天過著不穩定的生活，不過仍偶爾會與家人聯絡，當他的家人聽到這個噩耗時，簡直不敢相信他被活活打死。2名男童目前已被警方管護管束，待法官審判過後才能決定是送到精神院接受治療，或是送到教養學校。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6T9TeZL2jq4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6T9TeZL2jq4&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=76a3e3b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6T9TeZL2jq4</a>"},{"pid":"72f7919aa26c53f412f1b0085d2824164e535deb","tid":1674174,"uid":77355,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:11:48.000Z","msg":"好痴線"},{"pid":"9d0a055fa51c45f06dd4e663981f213f68245602","tid":1674174,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:13:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f448fa4deb4f04590b4bb6f7d724776c2a0d62a","tid":1674174,"uid":122134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:14:46.000Z","msg":"點做得出<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢啲應該拎去打把<br />\n大個啲真係不得了"},{"pid":"417b30ce7c5aef0d6ce3188b14dce3a7cab51c70","tid":1674174,"uid":189109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:15:08.000Z","msg":"如果生於香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d7a638c68f8cb0e2eaa386648f31624e886d6b0","tid":1674174,"uid":260694,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:27:37.000Z","msg":"經歷過革命，成長快左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7016cce8835d82fe8da1081f4cdfcf1c20104aa","tid":1674174,"uid":156891,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:36:42.000Z","msg":"不要搜尋3 guys 1 hammer <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bbd2bb698b1c51618918804e6410195f923f603","tid":1674174,"uid":13308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:55:48.000Z","msg":"變態"},{"pid":"36699538ecefd3aafdb788e28636f534430a1962","tid":1674174,"uid":150466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:58:53.000Z","msg":"好似寶馬山果單咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee637e767fd6c27678c5ee046aa2051948b356f3","tid":1674174,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:03:15.000Z","msg":"點解世畀無時無刻都有呢啲癲佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c209900c5e482470d8efc559ad549dafe58865","tid":1674174,"uid":69741,"like":1,"dislik